/// `/` opens the cockpit's popup search across todos and scratchpads. There is
/// no stock Zellij binding to retarget (locked mode passes raw keys to the
/// focused program), so this is appended into the locked block by
/// [`locked_extra_binds`]. The pipe is delivered to the Todos sidebar plugin,
/// which spawns the floating `panopt search` TUI. On sidebar plugin panes
/// (Normal mode), `/` is handled inside the plugin's own `handle_key` rather
/// than by Zellij - so the gesture works everywhere in the cockpit.
